column5: Hi everyone. I am planning to visit a BoQ this weekend. Is any bait shop around Belleville area? Thanks.
Quinte sports on hwy.62 1mile north of 401, Skevy's on hwy 2 just west of the river on the south side over the RR tracks.
Thank you. It's good location for me, but these guys are open from 8 am. Do you know some other place where i can get minnows i would say around 6 am?
I think Skevys is open at 6am.Give him a call 1(613)969-1035  just to make sure.
Quinte Sports is open at 6am Fri.Sat.Sun. 8 am the rest of the week.Skevy open at 6am closed on Mondays.
Moons in desanroto is open early....
